comment: Really terrible service. I don't recommend this place to anyone. It was an absolute waste of my money.
It was ok, but I thought it was too expensive. I expected much more for the amount I paid.
The service was ok, but I didn't really like the venue. The area was not clean and not maintained properly. I won't recommend this to anyone.
The service was fantastic, I totally recommend this place to everyone looking for a fun day out. Great prices, great selections, and amazing staff!
My experience here was amazing! A little too pricey, but quite decent value for money.
